These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
5 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, snooker, mah-jongg, chess
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, taxi, tram, van, boat
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person playing billiard##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the person driving the taxi and the person playing chess##2
12. the person driving the van is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
13. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Game   | snooker     | backgammon      | mah-jongg | chess   | billiard    |
| Transport   | van  | taxi     | car | tram | boat  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

