.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, architect, software-developer, scientist, nurse
House: gothic-revival, modern, tower, farmhouse, futuristic
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, indian, polish, spanish
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the futuristic house is on the left of the firefighter##1
 3. the architect is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the nurse is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the chinese and the futuristic house##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the architect##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the indian is the farmhouse house##1
 9. the indian is on the right of the architect##1
10. the tower house is on the right of the modern house##1
11. the indian is the software-developer##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Job         | scientist | firefighter | nurse    | architect  | software-developer    |
| House   | futuristic    | modern       | tower      | gothic-revival | farmhouse        |
| Nationality   | spanish   | dutch     | chinese    | polish  | indian     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

