.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, august, november, february, december
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, fisherman, journalist, teacher, accountant
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, rowing, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the police-officer is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the teacher##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the accountant and the person who's birthday is in november##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Birthday         | april | december     | november   | august   | february |
| Job   | accountant  | fisherman | police-officer | teacher | journalist        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball  | tennis    | badminton    | rowing        |

