The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, funk, indie, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 4. the pakistani is between the fan of reggae and the person traveling to paris##2
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the fan of funk##1
 9. the fan of rock is in the middle##1
10. the fan of reggae is the british##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
12. the british is on the right of the fan of indie##1
13. the fan of funk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| City          | hannover  | hamburg     | paris   | miami     | rome |
| Sport         | lacrosse | skiing    | baseball  | weightlifting | sailing   |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | dubstep    | rock     | indie     | reggae    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

