 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person driving the skateboard##2
 5. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the wooden house##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
12. the art-deco house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
13. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
