 3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person playing go is on the right of the french##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is between the person watching zombie movies and the person eating pomegranate##2
 7. the person eating nectarine is the turkish##1
 8. the australian is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the french##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching zombie movies and the person eating pomegranate##2
12. the person playing domino is on the right of the polish##1
13. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
