10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
13. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

