.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
The people have 5 different jobs:  teacher, pilot, software-developer, architect, nurse
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, oliveros, swisher, bluemaster
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, train, trike, van
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is between the person driving the quad-bike and the dunhill-smoker##2
 2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the architect##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the architect is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the software-developer is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the teacher is on the left of the software-developer##1
10. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the oliveros-smoker and the software-developer##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the nurse##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Job       | nurse | teacher | software-developer  | architect | pilot    |
| Cigar       | oliveros        | swisher   | dunhill  | bluemaster   | cain |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, iced-tea, milk, sprite
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, trike, roller, scooter, car
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, baseball, ice-hockey, surfing, skateboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching crime movies and the person driving the roller##2
 3. the person drinking milk is the person driving the scooter##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the car and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | cola         | milk      | iced-tea | sprite     |
| Transport           | trike | roller | scooter | car    | helicopter  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Sport   | ice-hockey  | baseball        | skiing   | surfing    | skateboarding     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
5 different games are played: domino, bridge, go, billiard, poker
The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, freelancer, architect, fisherman, journalist
5 different pets are kept: cat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, helicopter, jet-ski, ship
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the fisherman is on the left of the freelancer##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is between the mechanic and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the mechanic is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing go is between the person driving the airplane and the person playing poker##2
 8. the person playing bridge is between the person playing billiard and the person playing domino##2
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing domino##1
10. the person playing domino is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Game         | poker  | go | billiard   | bridge      | domino |
| Job   | mechanic   | fisherman    | freelancer | journalist | architect      |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | goldfish    | cat       | lizard     | mouse      |
| Transport     | helicopter | ship        | airplane  | car        | jet-ski    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, tulip, zinnia, poppy, orchid
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: august, july, april, june, january
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, electronic, reggae, rock
There are 5 different nationalities: american, australian, egyptian, malaysian, thai
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is between the malaysian and the fan of rock##2
 3. the fan of rock is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the fan of ambient is between the thai and the fan of electronic##2
 6. the thai is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in april is the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is the fan of blues##1
 9. the american is the fan of blues##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the egyptian##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
12. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Flower         | zinnia    | orchid  | tulip  | daffodil      | poppy |
| Birthday   | july    | january   | june | april | august   |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | ambient    | rock    | reggae       | blues         |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | australian | thai    | egyptian     | american      |

 